highlights.text: YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “เจิดจรัส” is the highest at #4.
“เมื่อไหร่จะบอก” by ETC. and The Parkinson is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #134.
“เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1253 days straight.
“ธารารัตน์” by YOUNGOHM is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 63 spots at #124.
